; sqmx_spin: spin (Ising) 2-variable model with zero coefficients
; evaluated against the default-initialised spin sample. Exercises
; SQMX + SSMX + ENERGY. Pair with sqmx_nonzero_linear for the
; non-trivial case that depends on the canonical [-1, ..., -1]
; default (QUI-453).

PUSH 2
SQMX r0

PUSH 2
SSMX r1

ENERGY r0 r1
STOW r2
PUSH 0
OUTPUT r2
HALT
